These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, basketball
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Sport   | biathlon | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Birthday   | january | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, water
1. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Beverage   | water | juice |

 #################################

 
